'''Sri Shakthi Institute of Engineering & Technology''' ('''SIET''') is an engineering institute located in [[Coimbatore]], [[Tamil Nadu]], India. Established in 2006,{{cn|date=March 2019}} it is affiliated to [[Anna University]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Affiliated colleges in Coimbatore District |url=https://www.annauniv.edu/cai/District%20wise/district/Coimbatore.php |website=annauniv.edu |accessdate=27 March 2019}}</ref> {{As of|2019}}, four of its programmes are accredited by the [[National Board of Accreditation]] (NBA).<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nbaind.org/accreditedprograms.aspx|title=National Board of Accreditation|website=www.nbaind.org|access-date=2019-03-27}}</ref>

